    b.  IN 1950 Someone got an idea to build a data science model which is loosely inspired by human mind.
        That Data science model is called Neural Network.
    c.  The idea was, it's rather than one statical program it was lots of statical programs they were
        all kinda a connected to gather in some way.
    d.  Same like Human neurons, The Neural Network has a lot of little algorithms called Artificial Neurons that are
        all connected to geather. It turn out to be effective way of learn different patterns from the data..
        for example: predicting the credit score by comparing your data with lot of other people
        data in calculating credit scores.
    e.  They had a break-through work with larger Neural Networks that could take more data and be able to detect the
