    a.  In 2019 these google scientists came up with a new way to organise these Neurons as Neural Network.
        They came up with a new architecture.
    b.  This new architecture was specially good while handling sequences of input and being able to look back on those
        sequences and figure out what parts of theses sequences are really matter which was a type of layer this
        network called self attention layer i.e attention layer.
    c.  This idea, the layer that was able to figure out "what should I pay attention to in the input sequence".
        So this allowed them to work with much bigger Neural Networks and much bigger data sets in less time and
        scale more effectively.
    d.  THIS ARCHITECTURE IS CALLED TRANSFORMER


